The GSF model uses a translog production function:
\deqn{y_i = \alpha_0 + \delta'z_i + \alpha'(x_i + \theta_i) + \frac{1}{2}(x_i + \theta_i)'B(x_i + \theta_i) + u_{0i} + \varepsilon_{0i}}

